name: com.mobiledgex.sdk
description: The MobiledgeX Client Library enables an application to register and then locate the nearest edge cloudlet backend server for use. The client library also allows verification of a device's location for all location-specific tasks.
description_zhCN: MobiledgeX客户端库使应用程序可以注册，然后找到最近的边缘cloudlet后端服务器以供使用。客户端库还允许针对所有特定于位置的任务验证设备的位置。
